WEBVTT

01:27.580 --> 01:31.930
[The Dark Romance]

01:32.160 --> 01:34.950
[Episode 14]

01:36.479 --> 01:37.140
Paw Patrol,

01:37.590 --> 01:39.590
my trip to Shenchuan
was definitely worth it.

01:39.590 --> 01:40.789
At least, now it is proven

01:40.789 --> 01:42.229
that the article "Edward Scissorhands"

01:42.229 --> 01:43.310
on the Amusement Park website

01:43.310 --> 01:44.840
is definitely a true story.

01:45.200 --> 01:47.000
This is Wei Zhihua's QQ photo album.

01:47.000 --> 01:48.509
Solid proof, isn't it?

01:49.759 --> 01:51.150
And do you know the password

01:51.150 --> 01:52.680
to her private photo album?

01:53.310 --> 01:54.560
It is the date

01:54.950 --> 01:56.680
when she and Edward Scissorhands

01:56.680 --> 01:59.560
fell in love,
as written in Mister's experiment diary—

01:59.560 --> 02:01.150
20110617.

02:01.590 --> 02:03.870
Doesn't this prove
that Mister didn't make anything up?

02:03.870 --> 02:05.350
A death was truly caused by him.

02:05.350 --> 02:06.750
The details all match up.

02:06.760 --> 02:07.880
This girl is dead.

02:08.110 --> 02:09.240
She killed herself.

02:09.470 --> 02:10.960
How are you not reacting to this?

02:10.960 --> 02:11.420
I-Isn't

02:11.470 --> 02:13.430
this enough to prove what happened?

02:13.430 --> 02:13.910
Look.

02:13.720 --> 02:16.300
[Support group
for victims of romance fraud]

02:14.630 --> 02:16.090
Previously, the TV station

02:16.090 --> 02:18.240
created this group chat
for victims of romantic fraud.

02:18.240 --> 02:19.400
I've asked the admin

02:19.400 --> 02:21.660
to send me all the victims' information.

02:21.680 --> 02:23.680
A girl named Mumu caught my attention.

02:23.680 --> 02:25.470
Her older sister had an identical

02:25.470 --> 02:26.329
Medusa tattoo.

02:26.910 --> 02:28.110
It really is the same.

02:30.190 --> 02:32.450
That man, "Mister," is surely ruthless.

02:32.630 --> 02:33.280
He alone could make

02:33.280 --> 02:34.840
so many girls commit suicide for him.

02:34.840 --> 02:36.240
What gave him that right?

02:36.400 --> 02:38.000
I've reached out to Mumu.

02:38.520 --> 02:39.720
Her sister, Xie Ke,

02:40.310 --> 02:42.800
used to be a very promising figure skater,

02:43.120 --> 02:43.910
who won

02:43.910 --> 02:46.000
the championship
at the 5th Eurasian Youth Games.

02:46.000 --> 02:47.840
But Mumu was too young at the time,

02:47.840 --> 02:50.640
so she couldn't provide
much useful information.

02:50.710 --> 02:52.280
That said, I did manage to get the contact

02:52.280 --> 02:53.400
of her sister's partner.

02:53.400 --> 02:54.660
He's in Bingyuan City.

03:00.030 --> 03:01.150
Here's a reminder for you, though.

03:01.150 --> 03:02.360
A police case has not been opened

03:02.360 --> 03:03.460
or reported on this matter.

03:03.460 --> 03:05.260
So, you're not going to Bingyuan

03:05.280 --> 03:07.000
for an investigation, but just a fun trip

03:07.000 --> 03:08.370
during the vacation.

03:08.710 --> 03:09.190
Understood?

03:09.190 --> 03:09.520
Understood.

03:09.520 --> 03:10.850
Just a visit to friends.

03:14.780 --> 03:16.170
[A fallen star: the tragedy
of a 22-year-old figure skating champion]

03:14.960 --> 03:16.020
The year of 2011...

03:16.190 --> 03:17.300
[A farewell in Chengyu Gymnasium]

03:19.240 --> 03:21.329
Then the time of Xie Ke's suicide

03:21.470 --> 03:23.550
wasn't far off from Wei Zhihua's.

03:24.030 --> 03:24.710
You see,

03:26.030 --> 03:27.680
they both had that Medusa tattoo.

03:27.680 --> 03:28.810
Could it be possible

03:28.840 --> 03:29.750
that this tattoo

03:29.750 --> 03:31.560
is somewhat a personal symbol

03:32.240 --> 03:33.150
of Mister?

03:33.630 --> 03:34.520
It's like a stamp.

03:34.520 --> 03:36.240
When he stamps this mark on a woman,

03:36.240 --> 03:37.240
that woman becomes his.

03:37.240 --> 03:39.120
Why direct that gesture at me?

03:41.240 --> 03:42.190
If that's the case,

03:42.190 --> 03:43.910
Xia Yi actually had his victims

03:43.910 --> 03:44.870
get that octopus tattoo

03:44.870 --> 03:45.360
f-following

03:45.360 --> 03:46.840
Mister's modus operandi.

03:47.240 --> 03:48.150
Y-Your hair...

03:49.910 --> 03:50.510
My hair...

03:51.150 --> 03:53.030
It's fair to be called a work injury.

03:53.030 --> 03:54.630
W-When I met the barber,

03:54.630 --> 03:56.890
he immediately decided to give me a perm.

03:57.120 --> 03:58.590
You made quite a sacrifice, didn't you?

03:58.590 --> 03:59.680
This is not so bad.

03:59.800 --> 04:01.530
Is my hairstyle that terrible?

04:03.400 --> 04:04.460
Keep yourself safe

04:04.560 --> 04:05.740
when you're in Bingyuan.

04:05.740 --> 04:07.800
Avoid getting injured again at work.

04:12.310 --> 04:13.040
Okay, got it.

04:27.070 --> 04:27.870
Morning, everyone.

04:27.870 --> 04:28.680
-Morning.
-Morning.

04:28.680 --> 04:30.140
Here's something for you.

04:30.310 --> 04:31.310
My wedding candy.

04:32.200 --> 04:33.510
It's Dr. Luo's wedding candy.

04:33.510 --> 04:34.560
Who is the bride?

04:34.720 --> 04:35.310
Why the rush?

04:35.310 --> 04:36.070
We'll see her

04:36.070 --> 04:37.070
at the wedding, won't we?

04:37.070 --> 04:38.070
Come on, help yourselves.

04:38.070 --> 04:38.870
Let's all share the joy.

04:38.870 --> 04:40.530
Dr. Luo, when is your wedding?

04:42.480 --> 04:43.480
My love and I both hate the hassle,

04:43.480 --> 04:44.480
so we won't hold a wedding.

04:44.480 --> 04:45.070
Back to your work, ladies.

04:45.070 --> 04:46.270
It's time I started my shift.

04:46.270 --> 04:48.310
-When will we get to see the bride?
-When can we see the bride?

04:48.310 --> 04:50.310
I'll introduce her to you when I can.

04:52.920 --> 04:54.580
Patient No.13, Xu Feng—

04:54.750 --> 04:55.360
Xu Feng,

04:55.600 --> 04:57.159
please report to Room 6.

05:04.630 --> 05:05.960
What's wrong this time?

05:08.340 --> 05:09.470
Actually, I'm fine.

05:10.000 --> 05:12.260
I paid a registration fee just to see you.

05:12.750 --> 05:13.650
While I'm at it,

05:14.120 --> 05:16.920
I'd like you to enlighten me
on something, Senior.

05:18.620 --> 05:20.650
Since when have you become this humble?

05:20.650 --> 05:21.810
I'm not used to this.

05:22.330 --> 05:24.480
You've been saying
I don't know how to make a clean exit.

05:24.480 --> 05:25.430
I used to...

05:25.750 --> 05:27.010
object to it deep down.

05:27.950 --> 05:29.780
I already made Li Changning
attempt suicide.

05:29.780 --> 05:31.840
How did I not make a clean enough exit?

05:32.190 --> 05:34.120
But recently, by chance,

05:34.270 --> 05:35.470
I found a PUA master's

05:35.600 --> 05:36.950
secret manual,

05:38.040 --> 05:40.970
and finally realized the huge gap
between me and him.

05:45.390 --> 05:46.830
About encouraging suicide,

05:46.830 --> 05:47.960
this is what he says:

05:48.510 --> 05:50.170
the mediocre stab on their own

05:50.290 --> 05:52.430
and inevitably stain their hands
with blood.

05:52.430 --> 05:53.510
Experts prepare the knife

05:53.510 --> 05:54.600
and hand it over.

05:54.950 --> 05:56.450
But real masters are able to

05:56.450 --> 05:58.770
have their preys kill themselves
with the weapons on them

05:58.770 --> 06:00.430
and then walk away unscathed.

06:00.830 --> 06:01.530
It's hard,

06:02.000 --> 06:02.870
but not that hard,

06:02.870 --> 06:04.130
to achieve this level.

06:04.390 --> 06:05.430
It has to be known that a demon

06:05.430 --> 06:06.950
lives in everyone's heart.

06:06.950 --> 06:08.990
All we should do is release it

06:09.020 --> 06:10.820
and let it devour our old selves.

06:12.240 --> 06:13.370
Perfectly written,

06:14.050 --> 06:14.580
isn't it?

06:16.190 --> 06:17.630
Where did you read this?

06:19.270 --> 06:21.530
People online all say
this master has gone into hiding.

06:21.530 --> 06:24.130
All I could find were fragments
of his remarks.

06:26.160 --> 06:27.230
What a pity.

06:28.240 --> 06:29.240
See, he already discovered

06:29.240 --> 06:31.080
the secret of manipulating others.

06:31.080 --> 06:33.720
He could've enjoyed the ultimate pleasure
of being a god on earth,

06:33.720 --> 06:35.510
brought benefits to his vast followers,

06:35.510 --> 06:37.040
and received their adoration.

06:37.040 --> 06:38.770
Why would he suddenly retreat?

06:38.920 --> 06:40.520
Even his legends are fading.

06:40.520 --> 06:41.380
Why did he quit?

06:46.690 --> 06:47.420
I don't know.

06:48.110 --> 06:50.040
I don't understand a word you said.

06:50.260 --> 06:52.220
You didn't pay
a registration fee of 600 yuan

06:52.220 --> 06:53.820
just to tell me this, did you?

07:02.190 --> 07:03.880
Ms. Yan's video has gone viral

07:05.010 --> 07:07.030
on the internet lately.

07:08.350 --> 07:10.300
Would you say her tragic story

07:11.150 --> 07:12.680
is the weapon

07:12.680 --> 07:13.870
you found on her?

07:14.940 --> 07:15.550
Xu Feng.

07:20.680 --> 07:22.620
If you don't have any other question,

07:22.620 --> 07:23.720
why not leave and stop

07:23.720 --> 07:25.450
hogging other patients' time?

07:31.810 --> 07:32.550
I'm sorry

07:33.040 --> 07:34.240
that I can't help you.

07:39.310 --> 07:40.370
Thank you, Dr. Luo.

07:40.890 --> 07:42.220
Every time after talking to you,

07:42.220 --> 07:43.880
I can see things in a new light.

07:57.480 --> 07:58.080
Sorry.

07:58.310 --> 07:59.510
Please give us a moment.

07:59.510 --> 07:59.870
Sure.

08:09.160 --> 08:10.280
I also found this.

08:19.430 --> 08:20.490
This fee of 600 yuan

08:20.600 --> 08:21.730
has paid for itself.

08:34.409 --> 08:35.940
Do you need my help to get up?

09:10.120 --> 09:12.390
Medusa,
a monstrous woman with snakes as hair,

09:12.390 --> 09:15.160
was originally a priestess
in the temple of Athena.

09:15.160 --> 09:17.310
She swore a vow of chastity for life.

09:18.080 --> 09:20.480
Yet seduced by Poseidon,
the god of the sea,

09:20.480 --> 09:22.450
she turned into a debauched woman

09:22.510 --> 09:24.710
having an affair with him in the temple.

09:26.140 --> 09:28.120
From then on, any man who saw her face

09:28.120 --> 09:29.450
would become stones.

09:30.480 --> 09:31.600
Am I right,

09:32.020 --> 09:32.750
Mister?

09:43.970 --> 09:45.720
I knew you'd come find me.

09:50.540 --> 09:52.000
How did you get that photo?

09:55.150 --> 09:57.280
Xie Ke's sister is as beautiful as her.

09:57.690 --> 09:59.030
As stupid as her, too.

09:59.790 --> 10:01.960
I flew to Bingyuan,
bought her a bubble tea,

10:01.960 --> 10:03.650
and she told me everything.

10:04.750 --> 10:05.510
Besides...

10:08.360 --> 10:09.820
She showed me this as well.

10:16.630 --> 10:17.890
She strongly suspects

10:18.070 --> 10:19.990
the man with a watch in this photo,

10:20.470 --> 10:23.470
just like the tattoo
that suddenly appeared on Xie Ke,

10:24.000 --> 10:26.400
was a secret
that her sister couldn't tell.

10:27.360 --> 10:29.150
This man was even probably related

10:29.150 --> 10:29.910
to her death.

10:31.910 --> 10:33.670
Do you know which discovery excited me

10:33.670 --> 10:34.320
most?

10:43.030 --> 10:44.440
In fact, upon seeing that photo,

10:44.440 --> 10:46.100
I was eager to ask you about it.

10:46.220 --> 10:47.550
But I held back the urge.

10:47.960 --> 10:48.910
I also wanted to find out

10:48.910 --> 10:50.640
if I was really inferior to you.

10:50.740 --> 10:53.360
Then I started searching everywhere
for that Medusa tattoo.

10:53.360 --> 10:54.690
It took me quite a while.

10:55.200 --> 10:55.760
Finally,

10:56.200 --> 10:57.800
on an overseas online forum,

10:58.360 --> 11:00.120
I saw someone mourning

11:00.120 --> 11:02.140
for a long-closed pickup website.

11:03.000 --> 11:04.150
There was a master

11:05.080 --> 11:06.610
named "Mister."

11:06.790 --> 11:08.220
He shared several

11:08.360 --> 11:10.220
highly impressive PUA examples.

11:10.720 --> 11:11.920
One of them was called

11:12.630 --> 11:14.150
"The Snow Queen."

11:15.910 --> 11:17.370
The master was you, right?

11:20.440 --> 11:21.900
What a fascinating story.

11:23.390 --> 11:24.850
You should write fiction.

11:28.800 --> 11:30.880
How can fiction be compared with this?

11:30.880 --> 11:33.010
It was a miracle that truly took place.

11:34.440 --> 11:35.200
Too bad

11:36.510 --> 11:38.970
that the genius
who made that miracle happen

11:39.120 --> 11:41.520
doesn't even have the courage
to own it now.

11:42.230 --> 11:43.000
I heard

11:43.000 --> 11:45.460
the Amusement Park was shut down
at its peak.

11:46.840 --> 11:47.510
Why?

11:49.030 --> 11:50.560
Wasn't it heart-breaking?

11:52.690 --> 11:55.420
I know what made Mister
close the Amusement Park.

11:59.820 --> 12:00.940
It was fear.

12:04.850 --> 12:07.180
When Yuan Ye stabbed me
with a bottle opener,

12:07.180 --> 12:08.840
I felt fear for the first time.

12:10.290 --> 12:12.090
You shared that feeling, right,

12:15.510 --> 12:16.320
Mister?

12:23.120 --> 12:26.780
[Lihai University
of Finance and Economics]

14:01.270 --> 14:03.730
My mom is asking
when we can meet your mother.

14:04.600 --> 14:06.200
My mom is a great fan of yours.

14:06.550 --> 14:08.480
I hope your mother
will be happy with me too.

14:08.230 --> 14:09.690
[Dial]

14:19.100 --> 14:19.580
[Dial]

14:19.630 --> 14:21.500
[Dialing]

14:21.530 --> 14:26.570
[The call is ringing]

14:26.690 --> 14:29.730
[Call in progress]
[Lihai Mobile]

14:29.150 --> 14:29.630
Hello?

14:31.550 --> 14:32.240
Su?

14:35.120 --> 14:36.000
Is that you, Su?

14:39.720 --> 14:40.580
What happened?

14:47.440 --> 14:48.300
What happened?

14:51.080 --> 14:52.080
Su?

14:59.750 --> 15:00.560
Su?

15:02.280 --> 15:02.990
Su?

15:02.410 --> 15:08.390
[Call in progress]
[Lihai Mobile]

15:34.480 --> 15:35.410
Hello, Dr. Luo!

15:35.600 --> 15:36.400
There you are.

15:39.400 --> 15:39.830
Mom.

15:44.840 --> 15:46.040
Where is your mother?

15:46.790 --> 15:47.720
In the bathroom.

15:47.890 --> 15:48.840
She said she felt a bit nervous

15:48.840 --> 15:50.240
and wanted to freshen up.

15:51.830 --> 15:53.360
What happened to your hand?

15:54.440 --> 15:54.970
Nothing.

15:55.120 --> 15:56.200
Just a minor injury.

15:56.200 --> 15:58.150
A patient kicked up a fuss
about being discharged.

15:58.150 --> 15:59.430
But it's all sorted now.

15:59.430 --> 16:00.280
Luo,

16:00.630 --> 16:03.010
your job is quite dangerous.

16:05.860 --> 16:06.280
Mom,

16:06.870 --> 16:09.870
such emergencies are unavoidable
in our department.

16:09.960 --> 16:10.890
But don't worry.

16:11.060 --> 16:12.920
For the sake of Yan Ling and Jiale,

16:13.020 --> 16:14.550
I will protect myself well.

16:17.090 --> 16:17.710
Mom.

16:19.590 --> 16:20.990
You're all here already.

16:21.600 --> 16:22.600
Welcome.

16:22.630 --> 16:23.080
Nice to meet you.

16:23.080 --> 16:23.750
Nice to meet you too,

16:23.750 --> 16:24.440
Mrs. Yan.

16:25.390 --> 16:26.850
This must be Jiale, right?

16:27.560 --> 16:29.090
What a handsome little boy.

16:29.120 --> 16:30.450
Thank you, Grandma Luo.

16:31.150 --> 16:32.350
Just call me Grandma.

16:33.630 --> 16:34.230
Thank you,

16:34.250 --> 16:34.790
Grandma.

16:36.190 --> 16:38.650
I can immediately tell he's well-mannered.

16:38.810 --> 16:40.810
You've done a good job teaching him.

16:42.120 --> 16:43.670
Ling looks even prettier in person

16:43.670 --> 16:45.600
than in the photos.

16:46.350 --> 16:48.320
Don't you dare bully her in the future.

16:48.320 --> 16:49.920
If you do, I won't let you off.

16:50.950 --> 16:52.550
I only have one older sister,

16:52.790 --> 16:55.600
who got married and moved
to the Philippines when she was young.

16:55.600 --> 16:58.200
Unexpectedly, her husband
passed away early.

16:58.270 --> 17:00.000
They didn't have any children.

17:00.590 --> 17:03.200
Not long ago, she was diagnosed
with lung cancer.

17:03.200 --> 17:04.750
and needed immediate surgery.

17:04.750 --> 17:06.550
There's no one to take care of her.

17:06.550 --> 17:07.200
So, today,

17:07.329 --> 17:10.510
I must apologize to you in advance
for not being able

17:11.030 --> 17:12.550
to stay too long with you.

17:13.030 --> 17:14.560
Illness is no small matter.

17:14.660 --> 17:15.859
Just go attend to her.

17:17.109 --> 17:18.109
I'm just sorry

17:18.349 --> 17:20.280
that I can't make it to the wedding.

17:22.030 --> 17:22.540
Mom.

17:23.680 --> 17:25.589
Neither Yan Ling nor I like crowds.

17:25.589 --> 17:26.650
After discussion,

17:27.190 --> 17:28.990
we decided not to have a wedding.

17:29.200 --> 17:30.960
When Ling and Jiale
are on summer vacation,

17:30.960 --> 17:31.920
the three of us

17:31.920 --> 17:33.250
will go out on a fun trip.

17:34.870 --> 17:35.870
That sounds good.

17:36.640 --> 17:38.050
As long as the two of you are happy,

17:38.050 --> 17:39.030
we are happy.

17:39.030 --> 17:39.920
Right, Mrs. Luo?

17:39.920 --> 17:40.920
Yes, sure.

17:41.790 --> 17:42.320
Oh right.

17:43.550 --> 17:45.350
You don't have to hold a wedding,

17:45.510 --> 17:46.160
but

17:46.680 --> 17:49.010
you must accept this red envelope from me.

17:50.590 --> 17:51.790
The amount is 10,001,

17:52.590 --> 17:56.070
meaning that you're a one-in-ten-thousand
daughter-in-law.

17:56.070 --> 17:57.000
Come on, take it.

18:03.910 --> 18:04.510
Thank you,

18:05.200 --> 18:05.880
Mom.

18:08.350 --> 18:09.030
Terrific.

18:09.400 --> 18:11.070
Now I have a good daughter.

18:18.920 --> 18:21.320
The moving company will come this weekend.

18:25.890 --> 18:26.820
Anything wrong?

18:27.240 --> 18:28.700
You don't want to move yet?

18:28.720 --> 18:30.250
How about I move in with you?

18:34.020 --> 18:35.620
When we were dining just now,

18:36.440 --> 18:37.570
your mother said

18:37.680 --> 18:39.210
she wanted grandchildren.

18:39.830 --> 18:40.550
But...

18:44.070 --> 18:45.110
She was just saying it.

18:45.110 --> 18:46.370
Don't take it to heart.

18:47.680 --> 18:50.340
Didn't we talk about this
before we got married?

18:50.540 --> 18:53.270
We don't necessarily
have to have another child.

18:53.730 --> 18:55.130
Jiale is all that we need.

19:02.740 --> 19:04.790
I feel like none of this is real.

19:10.290 --> 19:12.150
I'm so happy that it feels unreal.

19:18.050 --> 19:19.310
Then make me a promise.

19:21.130 --> 19:23.190
No matter what happens in the future,

19:24.650 --> 19:25.910
you'll never leave me.

19:29.580 --> 19:30.710
You have my promise.

19:31.860 --> 19:33.120
I will never leave you.

19:44.200 --> 19:45.000
Open the door.

19:45.400 --> 19:46.720
Alright, walk ahead.

19:46.750 --> 19:47.640
Be careful.

19:49.030 --> 19:49.920
Get ready.

19:50.480 --> 19:51.270
One.

19:52.000 --> 19:52.920
Two.

19:53.400 --> 19:53.920
Three!

19:57.000 --> 19:58.200
This is so cool!

19:58.200 --> 19:59.400
It's a space capsule?

19:59.440 --> 20:00.920
Yes. When you sleep in this bed,

20:00.920 --> 20:02.890
you'll be sent to the outer space.

20:03.680 --> 20:04.170
Look,

20:04.400 --> 20:05.930
the walls will be painted soon.

20:05.930 --> 20:08.270
I've also ordered a desk for you.
It'll be placed here.

20:08.270 --> 20:10.000
The workers can't be left

20:10.070 --> 20:11.030
unsupervised.

20:11.270 --> 20:12.560
I'll monitor them for you.

20:12.560 --> 20:13.930
When the renovation is done,

20:13.930 --> 20:16.030
I'll move back to Yan Ling's apartment.

20:16.030 --> 20:17.350
When you guys get too busy,

20:17.350 --> 20:18.610
I'll look after Jiale.

20:20.170 --> 20:21.170
What matters most

20:21.590 --> 20:22.750
is the two of you

20:22.920 --> 20:23.980
living a good life.

20:25.310 --> 20:25.920
Mom.

20:28.070 --> 20:28.550
Mom,

20:29.070 --> 20:30.270
this is your home too.

20:30.590 --> 20:32.240
You're welcome to come over anytime.

20:32.240 --> 20:32.810
Okay.

20:33.720 --> 20:34.450
Well then...

20:34.480 --> 20:36.510
I'll go clean up the study
for Jiale to stay in.

20:36.510 --> 20:36.960
Okay.

20:45.440 --> 20:46.640
I'll help Mom with it.

20:47.960 --> 20:48.540
Mom,

20:48.830 --> 20:49.790
let me help you with it.

20:49.790 --> 20:50.270
Okay.

20:51.510 --> 20:52.640
I feel like...

20:52.660 --> 20:54.660
Grandma is a bit different now.

20:55.550 --> 20:56.240
Is she?

20:56.480 --> 20:57.550
Different how?

20:58.020 --> 21:01.300
When she saw me getting coke
from the fridge yesterday,

21:01.830 --> 21:02.960
she didn't scold me.

21:03.380 --> 21:05.880
Instead, she replaced it
with a can at room temperature.

21:05.880 --> 21:07.270
What are you laughing at?

21:07.270 --> 21:10.000
I'm just relieved
that you two no longer quarrel.

21:16.030 --> 21:17.960
I've made peace with your grandma.

21:18.240 --> 21:18.990
We...

21:19.590 --> 21:21.000
won't fight anymore.

21:22.590 --> 21:23.850
Better keep your word.

21:25.160 --> 21:25.890
Come with me.

21:26.680 --> 21:28.340
Let me show you one more thing.

21:28.510 --> 21:30.890
Uncle Luo prepared it for you.

21:33.550 --> 21:35.030
Remove the cloth and take a look.

21:35.030 --> 21:35.830
You mean this?

21:40.710 --> 21:42.200
A mansion for Cola?

21:42.350 --> 21:43.190
Do you like it?

21:43.350 --> 21:43.960
Yes.

21:46.550 --> 21:47.450
I can put

21:47.480 --> 21:48.560
a swing here.

21:51.910 --> 21:52.920
But I don't want to move Cola

21:52.920 --> 21:55.180
into this mansion until a few days later.

21:56.440 --> 21:57.450
Why?

21:58.570 --> 22:00.170
Do you not like your new home?

22:01.920 --> 22:04.580
I want to spend some days
with my dad at his place.

22:06.790 --> 22:07.450
Why is that?

22:09.510 --> 22:11.000
Now, both Dr. Luo

22:11.960 --> 22:13.360
and Grandma are with you.

22:13.480 --> 22:14.740
But my dad is all alone.

22:15.030 --> 22:16.960
Even Ms. Fang Fang is ignoring him.

22:18.000 --> 22:19.000
I feel bad for him.

22:25.030 --> 22:26.490
Well, then spend more time

22:26.510 --> 22:27.480
with your dad

22:27.750 --> 22:28.680
these days,

22:28.880 --> 22:29.440
okay?

22:35.680 --> 22:36.550
I'm sorry.

22:38.280 --> 22:39.720
You're still a kid,

22:41.240 --> 22:44.640
yet you have to always
take us adults' feelings into account.

22:44.830 --> 22:46.030
It must be hard on you.

22:49.000 --> 22:49.830
Actually,

22:50.350 --> 22:52.750
my dad and I haven't finished
that game yet.

22:53.820 --> 22:55.900
If Grandma sees us playing games,

22:56.590 --> 22:59.190
I'm afraid she'll go back
to how she was before.

23:00.110 --> 23:00.640
Will she?

23:30.320 --> 23:31.560
[Introduction to Marine Science]

23:30.790 --> 23:33.600
Ling's father spent most of his life
at sea,

23:34.240 --> 23:36.830
so she has loved going to the beach
since she was little,

23:36.830 --> 23:39.290
saying that it could bring her
closer to him.

23:39.790 --> 23:40.720
When she grew up,

23:41.070 --> 23:42.000
she also picked a major

23:42.000 --> 23:43.360
related to the ocean.

23:53.850 --> 23:54.670
This...

23:55.480 --> 23:57.280
was a gift from Ling's dad to her.

23:57.310 --> 23:58.570
She treasures it a lot.

24:01.750 --> 24:02.610
It's so pretty.

24:06.350 --> 24:06.830
Mom.

24:09.200 --> 24:10.330
You finally woke up.

24:10.640 --> 24:11.790
I'll put it on the bookcase for you.

24:11.790 --> 24:12.310
Okay.

24:12.400 --> 24:13.070
Alright.

24:13.550 --> 24:15.270
Take a rest. Enough with the work now.

24:15.270 --> 24:16.170
Food is ready.

24:16.270 --> 24:17.030
I asked Luo Liang to eat first,

24:17.030 --> 24:18.960
yet he insisted on waiting for you.

24:19.240 --> 24:19.840
Yes, I did.

24:22.030 --> 24:22.770
This is for you.

24:22.770 --> 24:23.270
It's hot.

24:23.270 --> 24:23.810
Hot it is.

24:24.070 --> 24:24.610
So hot.

24:25.100 --> 24:26.030
Mom, take a seat.

24:29.420 --> 24:31.820
It's just the way you liked it
when you were a kid—

24:31.820 --> 24:32.710
a soft-boiled egg

24:32.710 --> 24:33.710
without vinegar.

24:34.720 --> 24:36.030
Does this suit your taste?

24:36.030 --> 24:36.760
Let me try it.

24:41.440 --> 24:42.370
It's delicious.

24:43.830 --> 24:45.790
It tastes exactly like when I was a kid.

24:45.790 --> 24:47.350
It's good. It really is good.

24:47.350 --> 24:48.490
Then have some more.

24:51.590 --> 24:52.590
I heard from Jiale

24:52.640 --> 24:54.640
that you make amazing braised pork.

24:54.880 --> 24:57.140
I wonder
if I'll have a chance to taste it.

24:57.790 --> 24:58.590
Okay.

24:59.200 --> 25:00.800
I'll make braised pork then.

25:03.370 --> 25:05.230
[Bingyuan City]

25:04.820 --> 25:06.990
Come buy Bingyuan chicken carcasses!

25:12.350 --> 25:14.430
Bingyuan chicken carcasses!

25:18.540 --> 25:20.680
Bingyuan chicken carcasses!

25:21.060 --> 25:22.030
Hey, sir!

25:22.720 --> 25:23.380
Take a seat.

25:24.000 --> 25:24.530
Qiu Dong!

25:25.280 --> 25:26.740
Haven't you drunk enough?

25:27.550 --> 25:28.000
Honey,

25:28.000 --> 25:28.720
I wasn't drinking.

25:28.720 --> 25:30.030
I was cultivating a customer base.

25:30.030 --> 25:31.750
Can't you have a long-term perspective?

25:31.750 --> 25:33.410
What long-term perspective?

25:33.750 --> 25:35.270
Look what you're like now.

25:35.290 --> 25:36.490
I'll be with you soon.

25:39.110 --> 25:39.920
Are you...

25:40.400 --> 25:41.110
Qiu Dong?

25:42.600 --> 25:43.680
Yes, also nicknamed...

25:43.680 --> 25:44.340
the Prince.

25:46.000 --> 25:47.270
Care for some pork skirt?

25:47.270 --> 25:47.890
Two pieces.

25:47.890 --> 25:48.440
Okay.

25:48.550 --> 25:49.410
I'll take them.

25:50.070 --> 25:51.270
Come on, let me fill your glass.

25:51.270 --> 25:52.920
We just prepared a few dishes.

25:52.920 --> 25:53.680
That's nice.

25:54.010 --> 25:57.460
[House specialty barbecue]

25:54.770 --> 25:55.750
Hey, honey,

25:56.260 --> 25:57.870
my friend here came from afar.

25:57.870 --> 25:59.270
I must have a good chat with him.

25:59.270 --> 26:00.270
Okay. Eat up.

26:00.270 --> 26:01.000
Let me know if you need more.

26:01.000 --> 26:01.440
Okay.

26:01.440 --> 26:02.170
Remember it.

26:02.750 --> 26:04.210
Thanks for your hard work.

26:07.370 --> 26:08.550
Come on, a toast to you.

26:07.430 --> 26:11.180
[House specialty barbecue]

26:09.310 --> 26:09.770
Cheers.

26:10.270 --> 26:10.880
Well,

26:10.900 --> 26:12.280
when you called me earlier,

26:12.280 --> 26:13.400
I thought you were a fraud.

26:13.400 --> 26:14.350
Sorry about that.

26:14.350 --> 26:16.210
I'll drink this up out of respect.

26:21.640 --> 26:22.790
Ke's death

26:22.790 --> 26:24.210
was many years ago.

26:25.160 --> 26:27.090
Has something new about it come up?

26:27.260 --> 26:27.710
No.

26:28.880 --> 26:30.550
I'm just curious about

26:31.000 --> 26:31.930
the competition

26:32.640 --> 26:34.240
Xie Ke attended before her death—

26:34.240 --> 26:36.100
the one you guys made a mistake in.

26:36.400 --> 26:37.730
What exactly happened?

26:52.580 --> 26:53.640
It was all my fault.

26:54.680 --> 26:57.880
I really wish I could apologize to her
in the netherworld.

26:59.370 --> 27:00.800
I don't know much.

27:00.830 --> 27:01.450
But...

27:01.960 --> 27:03.240
aren't mistakes common

27:03.240 --> 27:05.650
in figure skating competitions?

27:06.720 --> 27:07.750
How was that one

27:08.310 --> 27:09.500
so serious?

27:11.240 --> 27:13.240
Actually, before the competition,

27:13.270 --> 27:14.480
we had a quarrel,

27:15.240 --> 27:16.700
which affected Ke's mood.

27:17.480 --> 27:19.080
Because of the competition?

27:23.160 --> 27:24.620
Because of her boyfriend.

27:28.010 --> 27:31.060
It was about half a year before Ke's death

27:31.230 --> 27:34.440
when I first found out
she was dating someone.

27:35.030 --> 27:36.080
A company invited

27:36.480 --> 27:38.070
our whole team to perform.

27:43.620 --> 27:44.200
Qiu Dong!

27:45.070 --> 27:45.680
Hurry up!

27:45.680 --> 27:46.000
Coach!

27:46.000 --> 27:47.460
The bus is leaving in a sec.

27:50.000 --> 27:50.480
Well,

27:50.640 --> 27:52.000
Ke is catching up on sleep, right?

27:52.000 --> 27:54.000
I'll hail a cab and go with her later.

27:54.350 --> 27:55.110
Oh, you.

27:55.640 --> 27:56.240
Off you go!

27:57.540 --> 27:58.800
Come on, get on the bus.

28:00.770 --> 28:01.400
Bring my bag there.

28:01.400 --> 28:02.070
Hurry!

28:06.240 --> 28:07.030
She didn't answer

28:07.030 --> 28:07.570
my calls

28:08.480 --> 28:09.640
or stay in her room,

28:09.960 --> 28:11.490
so I went out to look for her.

28:12.830 --> 28:13.900
Are you Xie Ke?

28:14.680 --> 28:15.620
Are you Xie Ke?

28:15.650 --> 28:16.270
W-Who are you?

28:16.270 --> 28:17.670
Can you please leave him?

28:17.880 --> 28:19.500
What are you talking about?

28:19.880 --> 28:21.340
You are Xie Ke, aren't you?

28:21.640 --> 28:22.850
Get out of my way.

28:22.880 --> 28:24.000
I am his girlfriend.

28:24.000 --> 28:25.470
I really am his girlfriend.

28:25.470 --> 28:26.600
I beg you. Please...

28:27.120 --> 28:28.500
Please don't break us up, okay?

28:28.500 --> 28:29.310
That woman was

28:29.960 --> 28:31.820
staring fiercely at Ke like this,

28:32.730 --> 28:34.530
as if she wanted to eat her alive.

28:35.160 --> 28:36.030
I'm begging you.

28:36.030 --> 28:37.240
Leave him alone, will you?

28:37.240 --> 28:38.960
-I beg you!
-You're hurting me!

28:38.960 --> 28:40.360
Give him back to me, okay?

28:40.560 --> 28:42.960
-Get up.
-I've been with him for a long time.

28:43.110 --> 28:44.480
I've abandoned my family

28:44.480 --> 28:45.840
and even my child.

28:46.070 --> 28:47.400
All I want is him.

28:47.420 --> 28:48.510
He's all I want.

28:49.730 --> 28:50.920
Give him back to me, will you?

28:50.920 --> 28:52.640
But he really has never told me

28:52.640 --> 28:53.640
that he has a girlfriend.

28:53.640 --> 28:54.640
I truly am.

28:55.790 --> 28:57.250
I truly am his girlfriend!

28:58.560 --> 28:59.320
I beg you...

29:00.550 --> 29:01.640
Ever since then,

29:02.480 --> 29:04.480
she started avoiding me on purpose.

29:04.680 --> 29:06.200
At that time, we were

29:06.750 --> 29:09.000
preparing for the Asian Championships.

29:09.000 --> 29:10.400
Except during training,

29:11.070 --> 29:13.000
she wouldn't say anything to do me.

29:20.680 --> 29:21.680
Give me a minute.

29:22.440 --> 29:23.240
What's wrong?

29:24.000 --> 29:25.600
Are you lacking confidence?

29:26.240 --> 29:26.680
I also think

29:26.680 --> 29:28.680
this triple throw jump is too difficult.

29:28.680 --> 29:30.280
Maybe we should play it safe.

29:30.480 --> 29:30.810
Look,

29:30.830 --> 29:31.590
I'll tell the coach

29:31.590 --> 29:33.030
about changing the choreography.

29:33.030 --> 29:34.110
I can do the jump.

29:35.000 --> 29:36.100
You may go back now.

29:36.400 --> 29:38.240
I'd like to practice alone for a while.

29:38.240 --> 29:40.000
But this is a pair skating move.

29:40.000 --> 29:41.350
How do you practice it alone?

29:41.350 --> 29:42.350
I can nail it.

29:42.350 --> 29:43.510
Off you go!

29:49.780 --> 29:51.150
Figure skaters like us

29:51.960 --> 29:53.420
usually grow up together,

29:55.480 --> 29:57.080
receive training together,

29:57.480 --> 29:58.310
eat together,

29:59.640 --> 30:01.700
and nearly spend every day together,

30:02.030 --> 30:04.090
except that we don't sleep together.

30:06.090 --> 30:08.350
Plus, there is so much physical contact.

30:09.310 --> 30:10.280
Her boyfriend

30:10.590 --> 30:11.640
must've felt upset about it,

30:11.640 --> 30:12.170
right?

30:13.640 --> 30:14.260
Wait.

30:14.350 --> 30:15.750
That doesn't make sense.

30:16.350 --> 30:17.400
He must have known it

30:17.400 --> 30:19.440
before they started dating.

30:19.830 --> 30:20.830
If he said he minded it

30:20.830 --> 30:22.350
only after the romance began,

30:22.350 --> 30:24.610
wasn't he picking a fight deliberately?

30:26.920 --> 30:29.200
I have a guilty conscience.

30:36.920 --> 30:39.380
You might laugh at me,
but I'm going to say it—

30:41.030 --> 30:42.440
I had always liked Ke.

30:45.960 --> 30:46.790
I thought

30:47.830 --> 30:50.000
we were destined to be together.

30:52.110 --> 30:53.440
I had it all planned out.

30:55.720 --> 30:57.760
When we won the championship again,

30:58.270 --> 30:59.800
I would tell her I loved her.

31:02.480 --> 31:03.740
Who would've known...

31:09.240 --> 31:11.040
So the two of you got in a fight...

31:12.010 --> 31:13.470
because of her boyfriend?

31:20.270 --> 31:21.670
Before the competition,

31:23.010 --> 31:24.340
I saw her take medicine.

31:26.790 --> 31:27.650
What medicine?

31:30.430 --> 31:31.560
What are you taking?

31:32.960 --> 31:33.880
Painkillers.

31:34.510 --> 31:35.070
For what?

31:35.310 --> 31:36.170
Period cramps.

31:37.110 --> 31:37.750
Why are you lying to me?

31:37.750 --> 31:39.750
Are you even on your period these days?

31:39.750 --> 31:40.680
As if you'd know.

31:48.990 --> 31:51.450
Does this have something to do
with that guy?

31:52.310 --> 31:53.000
Who?

31:53.890 --> 31:55.100
No need to hide it from me.

31:55.100 --> 31:55.960
I saw you talking

31:55.960 --> 31:57.220
to that woman that day.

31:57.350 --> 32:00.160
Are you involved with someone
who's in a relationship?

32:00.160 --> 32:01.110
I am not!

32:02.100 --> 32:03.860
You'd better not be!

32:05.310 --> 32:06.370
What is it with you?

32:06.750 --> 32:07.480
You're a brilliant young woman.

32:07.480 --> 32:08.440
Why be with someone who's taken?

32:08.440 --> 32:10.770
-Ruining yourself, aren't you?
-Stop it!

32:11.030 --> 32:12.160
You don't know anything

32:12.160 --> 32:13.210
about him or me!

32:13.590 --> 32:14.550
I don't?

32:14.550 --> 32:16.010
You're right that I don't!

32:16.480 --> 32:17.000
But I do know

32:17.000 --> 32:19.000
even the greatest love
can't be built on someone's death,

32:19.000 --> 32:20.730
for there will be retribution!

32:33.110 --> 32:33.720
Who?

32:34.680 --> 32:35.480
Who died?

32:38.240 --> 32:39.400
After the event,

32:42.270 --> 32:44.330
everyone but me went back to the team.

32:44.680 --> 32:47.110
A few good friends came to visit me,

32:47.920 --> 32:50.220
so I stayed an extra day at the hotel.

32:50.920 --> 32:52.830
When I checked out the next day...

32:53.020 --> 32:53.710
Hello.

32:53.960 --> 32:54.750
I'd like to check out.

32:54.750 --> 32:55.360
Okay.

32:55.480 --> 32:56.940
I saw police cars

32:57.240 --> 32:59.280
and ambulances at the hotel entrance.

32:59.280 --> 33:00.610
There was a large crowd.

33:00.920 --> 33:02.270
I was told that a woman died

33:02.270 --> 33:04.070
in one of the hotel rooms.

33:10.240 --> 33:11.100
Enough!

33:11.510 --> 33:12.960
I'll talk to him.

33:25.540 --> 33:26.400
How did she die?

33:26.830 --> 33:28.270
Was it homicide, suicide,

33:28.270 --> 33:29.130
or an accident?

33:29.540 --> 33:30.500
I don't know.

33:32.640 --> 33:33.770
During those days,

33:34.680 --> 33:36.740
I paid special attention to the news,

33:37.300 --> 33:39.360
but no criminal cases were reported.

33:43.110 --> 33:45.910
Do you mean Xie Ke didn't know about it
at that time?

33:49.310 --> 33:50.480
And that's where

33:51.680 --> 33:53.350
my biggest regret came from—

33:56.560 --> 33:57.430
I couldn't help

33:58.760 --> 34:00.890
but tell her about that woman's death.

34:01.350 --> 34:02.280
Upon hearing it,

34:03.950 --> 34:05.130
she was petrified.

34:05.860 --> 34:07.930
Why did I have to be so tactless?

34:09.550 --> 34:10.670
Why couldn't I just

34:10.760 --> 34:11.480
keep my mouth shut?

34:11.480 --> 34:12.320
Why must I spill the truth

34:12.320 --> 34:13.520
at that exact moment?

34:13.590 --> 34:14.550
I just couldn't zip it!

34:14.550 --> 34:15.230
I was so mouthy!

34:15.230 --> 34:16.510
Why did I have to tell Ke that?

34:16.510 --> 34:17.969
Stop. Don't act like this.

34:20.230 --> 34:20.760
You said

34:21.000 --> 34:23.530
Ke took painkillers
before the competition.

34:24.219 --> 34:25.929
Did you know she had a tattoo?

34:27.590 --> 34:28.989
She didn't have a tattoo.

34:29.880 --> 34:31.880
Yes, she did. She had one right here.

34:32.150 --> 34:32.960
It's Medusa,

34:33.000 --> 34:35.000
t-the woman with snakes on her head.

34:35.550 --> 34:36.750
That was impossible.

34:36.960 --> 34:38.190
Ke and I

34:38.840 --> 34:39.760
practiced

34:40.920 --> 34:42.719
the triple throw jump every day.

34:42.960 --> 34:44.489
That spot you mentioned...

34:45.320 --> 34:47.250
was where she took the most impact.

34:47.280 --> 34:49.080
Why would she get a tattoo there?

34:55.210 --> 34:58.470
That is to say, Xie Ke made a mistake
during the competition

34:59.250 --> 35:01.630
not entirely due to emotional distress.

35:03.240 --> 35:04.440
She took painkillers

35:04.440 --> 35:06.150
because she had just gotten a tattoo,

35:06.150 --> 35:08.170
and it hurt when you touched her.

35:09.800 --> 35:11.350
Why would she get a tattoo?

35:12.920 --> 35:14.130
An athlete

35:14.230 --> 35:16.780
can't possibly get such a big tattoo.

35:16.800 --> 35:18.230
It wasn't her idea,

35:18.230 --> 35:20.410
but her boyfriend's.

35:21.440 --> 35:22.240
Are you saying

35:22.670 --> 35:24.470
her boyfriend meant to harm her?

35:25.480 --> 35:26.740
And she gave up her life

35:27.110 --> 35:27.910
for a romance?

35:30.230 --> 35:32.030
I knew Ke best.

35:32.150 --> 35:35.270
She was not the kind of girl

35:35.440 --> 35:38.000
who would go to pieces over love.

35:38.110 --> 35:39.230
In the eyes of outsiders like us,

35:39.230 --> 35:41.360
she was probably just dating someone.

35:41.450 --> 35:42.670
But for Xie Ke,

35:42.670 --> 35:44.590
what she had wasn't love at all.

35:44.740 --> 35:47.440
Anyone chosen as prey by that bastard

35:47.710 --> 35:51.440
would feel nothing
but immense pain and torment.

35:52.630 --> 35:53.960
Think about that woman.

35:59.890 --> 36:00.820
What do you mean?

36:03.520 --> 36:04.920
She died too, didn't she?

36:07.140 --> 36:08.220
I get it.

36:10.340 --> 36:12.670
He could push a woman
to the point of death.

36:13.180 --> 36:16.180
Of course he could do the same
to another woman, right?

36:17.770 --> 36:20.200
Ke's death was actually caused by someone,

36:20.800 --> 36:21.320
right?

36:25.880 --> 36:26.920
Someone caused her death,

36:26.920 --> 36:27.600
right?

36:27.840 --> 36:29.360
Someone caused her death,

36:29.360 --> 36:30.190
right?

36:30.210 --> 36:31.940
What do you think you are doing?

36:32.750 --> 36:34.080
Are you out of your mind?

36:35.230 --> 36:37.560
If you don't want to be with me,
just say it!

36:40.290 --> 36:41.110
Look at you,

36:41.110 --> 36:42.440
lying on the ground now!

36:55.920 --> 36:56.980
That was the story.

36:58.110 --> 36:58.960
Qiu Dong said

36:59.960 --> 37:01.480
he felt he was completely responsible

37:01.480 --> 37:03.280
for Xie Ke's injury at that time.

37:03.710 --> 37:04.960
So he proposed marriage to her,

37:04.960 --> 37:06.560
with the idea of caring for her
for a lifetime.

37:06.560 --> 37:07.790
But he was rejected.

37:09.670 --> 37:10.800
Shortly after that,

37:10.890 --> 37:12.350
Xie Ke committed suicide.

37:12.630 --> 37:14.560
If it hadn't been for that bastard,

37:15.550 --> 37:17.680
everything would've been different.

37:19.550 --> 37:20.400
Do you know which hotel

37:20.400 --> 37:21.930
they stayed at in Bingyuan?

37:23.760 --> 37:24.320
Yes.

37:25.250 --> 37:30.000
[Xueyu Royal Hotel]

37:30.230 --> 37:30.960
I remember the incident

37:30.960 --> 37:32.110
you're talking about.

37:32.110 --> 37:33.130
The woman was named...

37:33.130 --> 37:33.790
He Xiao.

37:33.960 --> 37:34.960
She was from Diannan,

37:34.960 --> 37:36.840
with the same surname
as the notorious ancient official He Shen.

37:36.840 --> 37:37.550
Sir.

37:38.440 --> 37:39.360
Did she have

37:40.630 --> 37:41.840
a tattoo like this?

37:43.030 --> 37:43.760
Yes, she did!

37:43.760 --> 37:44.420
This was it!

37:44.630 --> 37:45.840
A head surrounded by snakes.

37:45.840 --> 37:46.710
How scary.

37:46.950 --> 37:49.150
Now that you mention it,
I recall everything.

37:49.150 --> 37:50.870
Look, she was from Diannan.

37:50.940 --> 37:51.960
But for unknown reasons,

37:51.960 --> 37:54.590
she came all the way
to this very city of Bingyuan.

37:54.590 --> 37:55.800
Strange, wasn't it?

37:56.590 --> 37:57.550
Are you sure...

37:58.440 --> 37:59.570
she died by suicide?

37:59.960 --> 38:01.220
Absolutely.

38:01.320 --> 38:02.400
At that time, the police

38:02.400 --> 38:05.200
conducted a thorough investigation
in the hotel.

38:05.280 --> 38:07.110
He Xiao came and booked a room herself,

38:07.110 --> 38:07.440
right?

38:07.440 --> 38:08.590
After a few days' stay,

38:08.590 --> 38:10.590
one night, she went back to her room alone

38:10.590 --> 38:11.840
and took her own life.

38:12.000 --> 38:14.960
She wasn't seen interacting with anyone
in the course.

38:14.960 --> 38:16.550
I was a server here at that time,

38:16.550 --> 38:18.920
and I had to go into her room
to change the sheets.

38:18.920 --> 38:19.800
It was so unlucky for me

38:19.800 --> 38:20.880
to run into something like that, right?

38:20.880 --> 38:22.590
The police questioned me for a long time.

38:22.590 --> 38:23.630
Then what happened?

38:23.630 --> 38:24.560
What do you mean?

38:25.030 --> 38:27.230
Did her family not come looking for her?

38:29.060 --> 38:29.510
I heard

38:29.510 --> 38:31.760
her husband later identified her body
at the police station

38:31.760 --> 38:33.710
and said he'd take it away the next day.

38:33.710 --> 38:35.800
But as the police called him again,
they found he had disappeared.

38:35.800 --> 38:37.150
You have such a good memory.

38:37.150 --> 38:38.480
It's been so many years.

38:39.400 --> 38:40.230
The incident

38:41.800 --> 38:43.020
and the way she died

38:43.150 --> 38:44.150
were too bizarre.

38:45.320 --> 38:46.520
Let me put it this way.

38:47.230 --> 38:49.290
The moment I pushed that door open...

38:50.580 --> 38:52.640
I knew I would never forget what I saw.

40:27.170 --> 40:31.360
[The Dark Romance]

40:41.990 --> 40:43.190
You want this, right?

40:43.800 --> 40:44.160
Okay.

40:55.360 --> 40:56.480
High-calcium milk for kids

40:56.480 --> 40:57.400
made with premium formulas.

40:57.400 --> 40:58.030
Free tasting.

40:58.030 --> 40:59.070
Come on, have a taste.

40:59.070 --> 41:00.070
Come try it, please.

41:00.070 --> 41:02.150
Haven't you acted
in any show lately, Ms. Zhang?

41:02.150 --> 41:03.350
Don't get me started.

41:03.880 --> 41:06.230
I couldn't even get a single line all day.

41:06.480 --> 41:08.480
So I have to do some odd jobs now, see?

41:08.630 --> 41:09.680
But let me tell you something.

41:09.680 --> 41:11.030
I feel like I'm getting
more and more relaxed

41:11.030 --> 41:12.280
and less and less nervous

41:12.280 --> 41:13.440
during acting recently.

41:13.440 --> 41:14.110
Really?

41:14.230 --> 41:15.180
Here comes a customer.
